title: Lív Poulsen
text:
Lív Finnbogadóttir Arge Poulsen (<a href="n%C3%A9e">née</a> Finnbogadóttir Arge; born 20 March 1997) is a Faroese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> midfielder who currently plays for <a href="Havnar%20B%C3%B3ltfelag%20%28Women%29">Havnar Bóltfelag</a>.
Honours.
Runners-up
